<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reservation Status Update</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .logo {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .message {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img class="logo" src="https://bangteg.github.io/images/dampit-trans-logo.png" alt="Company Logo">
            <h2>Reservation Status Update</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p class="message">Dear <%= user.firstName %> <%= user.lastName %>,</p>
            <p>Your reservation has been <strong>approved</strong> by the admin.</p>
            <p>Reservation Details:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Reservation ID:</strong> <%= reservation.id %></li>
                <li><strong>Pick-Up Date:</strong> <%= reservation.pickDate %></li>
                <li><strong>Drop-Off Date:</strong> <%= reservation.dropDate %></li>
                <li><strong>Pick-Up Location:</strong> <%= reservation.pickUp %></li>
                <li><strong>Drop-Off Location:</strong> <%= reservation.dropOff %></li>
                <li><strong>Vehicle:</strong> <%= vehicle.name %></li>
                <li><strong>Total Price:</strong> <%= reservation.totalPrice %></li>
                <li><strong>Unit:</strong> <%= reservation.unit %></li>
                <li><strong>Passenger:</strong> <%= reservation.passengers %></li>
            </ul>
            <p>Thank you for choosing our service. If you have any questions, feel free to contact us.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This email is sent to <%= user.email %>. If you received this in error, please ignore it.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
